<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="48" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,151,212]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[201,336,152,176]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">Etymology.</emphasis>
The new species name is derived from the Latin word “ 
<emphasis box="[958,1047,153,176]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">exterius</emphasis>
”, indicating that both pygofer processes distinctly twisted outwards in caudal view.
</paragraph>
